{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be professional and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EdTech Platform</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #2c3e50; /* Dark blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header .container {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 28px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #3498db; /* Brand Blue */\n        }\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 25px;\n        }\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: #3498db; /* Brand Blue */\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #3498db; /* Brand Blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #3498db; /* Brand Blue */\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e0e0e0;\n        }\n        .features {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n        }\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 40px;\n            color: #3498db; /* Brand Blue */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 22px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n        }\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #666;\n        }\n        .testimonials {\n            background-color: #eaf2f8; /* Light blue tint */\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .testimonials h2 {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n        }\n        .testimonial-carousel {\n            display: flex;\n            overflow-x: auto;\n            scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;\n            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n            justify-content: center;\n            padding-bottom: 20px; /* For scrollbar */\n        }\n        .testimonial-item {\n            flex: 0 0 500px; /* Fixed width for each testimonial */\n            scroll-snap-align: start;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            text-align: left;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n        .testimonial-item p {\n            font-style: italic;\n            color: #555;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n        }\n        .testimonial-item .author {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #3498db; /* Brand Blue */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #2c3e50; /* Dark blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n        /* Simple scrollbar styling for demonstration */\n        .testimonial-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar {\n            height: 8px;\n        }\n        .testimonial-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar-track {\n            background: #f0f0f0;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n        }\n        .testimonial-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n            background: #3498db; /* Brand Blue */\n            border-radius: 10px;\n        }\n        .testimonial-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {\n            background: #2980b9;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"logo\">EduSphere</div>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#features\">Features</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#testimonials\">Testimonials</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#\">About</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Unlock Your Learning Potential</h1>\n            <p>Empowering learners with innovative and accessible educational experiences.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Now</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Why Choose EduSphere?</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chalkboard-teacher\"></i>\n                    <h3>Expert Instructors</h3>\n                    <p>Learn from industry leaders and passionate educators.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Personalized Paths</h3>\n                    <p>Tailored learning journeys to suit your pace and goals.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-book-open\"></i>\n                    <h3>Vast Content Library</h3>\n                    <p>Access a diverse range of courses and resources.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                    <h3>Community Support</h3>\n                    <p>Connect with fellow learners and instructors.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"testimonials\" class=\"testimonials\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>What Our Learners Say</h2>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-carousel\">\n                <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                    <p>\"EduSphere has completely transformed how I approach learning. The courses are engaging and the platform is incredibly user-friendly.\"</p>\n                    <div class=\"author\">- Sarah Chen, Student</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                    <p>\"I was able to gain new skills that directly impacted my career. The flexibility of learning on my own schedule was a huge benefit.\"</p>\n                    <div class=\"author\">- David Miller, Professional</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                    <p>\"The community aspect is fantastic. I've met so many driven individuals and learned from their experiences as well.\"</p>\n                    <div class=\"author\">- Aisha Khan, Lifelong Learner</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 EduSphere. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic JavaScript for potential future interactivity, not strictly needed for this static layout\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}